# Static (hand-written, version-controlled) skill bundles. The skill-bundler
# at prepublish only manages its own slugs (wellplayed-react / wellplayed-api),
# so static slugs like `wellplayed-cli` survive every bundler run.
!packages/*/skills/wellplayed-cli/
